    "In 1951 Malraux expanded and reissued <em>La Psychologie de l'art</em> as the <em>Les Voix du silence</em>, including the new section, \"Les Metamorphoses d'Apollon.\"": [],
    "A two-volume picture book, <em>Le mus\u00e9e imaginaire de la sculpture mondiale</em> was initially published in 1952.": [],
